  <a href="/rephosting/status/231089542915039232" class="tweet-timestamp js-permalink js-nav js-tooltip" title="11:10 AM - 2 Aug 2012" ><span class="_timestamp js-short-timestamp " data-aria-label-part="last" data-time="1343931015" data-time-ms="1343931015000" data-long-form="true">2 Aug 2012</span></a>
</small>

          
          
      </div>


      
        <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--26px js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Our servers are now running Subversion 1.7.5, Git 1.7.11.4, and Mercurial 2.2.3.</p>

<h1 class="ProfileHeaderCard-name">
<a href="/rephosting"
class="ProfileHeaderCard-nameLink u-textInheritColor js-nav
">Repository Hosting</a>
</h1>

<h2 class="ProfileHeaderCard-screenname u-inlineBlock u-dir" dir="ltr">
<a class="ProfileHeaderCard-screennameLink u-linkComplex js-nav" href="/rephosting">@<span class="u-linkComplex-target">rephosting</span></a>
</h2>

<p class="ProfileHeaderCard-bio u-dir"

dir="ltr">We are an online hosting service for software project management tools. We specialize in hosting Trac, Subversion, Git, and Mercurial repositories.</p>

<p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--26px js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Check out our latest new features: http://repositoryhosting.com/blog.  We also have a major system upgrade this weekend.</p>

<div class="ProfileHeaderCard">
<h1 class="ProfileHeaderCard-name">
<a href="/rephosting"
class="ProfileHeaderCard-nameLink u-textInheritColor js-nav
">Repository Hosting</a>
</h1>

<h2 class="ProfileHeaderCard-screenname u-inlineBlock u-dir" dir="ltr">
<a class="ProfileHeaderCard-screennameLink u-linkComplex js-nav" href="/rephosting">@<span class="u-linkComplex-target">rephosting</span></a>
</h2>

<p class="ProfileHeaderCard-bio u-dir"

dir="ltr">We are an online hosting service for software project management tools. We specialize in hosting Trac, Subversion, Git, and Mercurial repositories.</p>

<p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--16px js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Fortunately, <a href="http://t.co/ifELQndFxp" rel="nofollow" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="http://RepositoryHosting.com" class="twitter-timeline-link" target="_blank" title="http://RepositoryHosting.com" ><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="js-display-url">RepositoryHosting.com</span><span class="invisible"></span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible">&nbsp;</span></span></a> was not affected by <a href="/hashtag/Heartbleed?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" ><s>#</s><b>Heartbleed</b></a>, as we were not running a vulnerable version of OpenSSL.</p>

<p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--26px js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Check out our latest new features: http://repositoryhosting.com/blog.  We also have a major system upgrade this weekend.</p>

<div class="ProfileHeaderCard">
<h1 class="ProfileHeaderCard-name">
<a href="/rephosting"
class="ProfileHeaderCard-nameLink u-textInheritColor js-nav
">Repository Hosting</a>
</h1>

<h2 class="ProfileHeaderCard-screenname u-inlineBlock u-dir" dir="ltr">
<a class="ProfileHeaderCard-screennameLink u-linkComplex js-nav" href="/rephosting">@<span class="u-linkComplex-target">rephosting</span></a>
</h2>

<p class="ProfileHeaderCard-bio u-dir"

dir="ltr">We are an online hosting service for software project management tools. We specialize in hosting Trac, Subversion, Git, and Mercurial repositories.</p>

<p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--16px js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Fortunately, <a href="http://t.co/ifELQndFxp" rel="nofollow" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="http://RepositoryHosting.com" class="twitter-timeline-link" target="_blank" title="http://RepositoryHosting.com" ><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="js-display-url">RepositoryHosting.com</span><span class="invisible"></span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible">&nbsp;</span></span></a> was not affected by <a href="/hashtag/Heartbleed?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" ><s>#</s><b>Heartbleed</b></a>, as we were not running a vulnerable version of OpenSSL.</p>

<p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--26px js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Check out our latest new features: http://repositoryhosting.com/blog.  We also have a major system upgrade this weekend.</p>

<div class="ProfileHeaderCard">
<h1 class="ProfileHeaderCard-name">
<a href="/rephosting"
class="ProfileHeaderCard-nameLink u-textInheritColor js-nav
">Repository Hosting</a>
</h1>

<h2 class="ProfileHeaderCard-screenname u-inlineBlock u-dir" dir="ltr">
<a class="ProfileHeaderCard-screennameLink u-linkComplex js-nav" href="/rephosting">@<span class="u-linkComplex-target">rephosting</span></a>
</h2>

<p class="ProfileHeaderCard-bio u-dir"

dir="ltr">We are an online hosting service for software project management tools. We specialize in hosting Trac, Subversion, Git, and Mercurial repositories.</p>

<p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--16px js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Fortunately, <a href="http://t.co/ifELQndFxp" rel="nofollow" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="http://RepositoryHosting.com" class="twitter-timeline-link" target="_blank" title="http://RepositoryHosting.com" ><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="js-display-url">RepositoryHosting.com</span><span class="invisible"></span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible">&nbsp;</span></span></a> was not affected by <a href="/hashtag/Heartbleed?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" ><s>#</s><b>Heartbleed</b></a>, as we were not running a vulnerable version of OpenSSL.</p>

<p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--26px js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Check out our latest new features: http://repositoryhosting.com/blog.  We also have a major system upgrade this weekend.</p>

<div class="ProfileHeaderCard">
<h1 class="ProfileHeaderCard-name">
<a href="/rephosting"
class="ProfileHeaderCard-nameLink u-textInheritColor js-nav
">Repository Hosting</a>
</h1>

<h2 class="ProfileHeaderCard-screenname u-inlineBlock u-dir" dir="ltr">
<a class="ProfileHeaderCard-screennameLink u-linkComplex js-nav" href="/rephosting">@<span class="u-linkComplex-target">rephosting</span></a>
</h2>

<p class="ProfileHeaderCard-bio u-dir"

dir="ltr">We are an online hosting service for software project management tools. We specialize in hosting Trac, Subversion, Git, and Mercurial repositories.</p>

<p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--16px js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Fortunately, <a href="http://t.co/ifELQndFxp" rel="nofollow" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="http://RepositoryHosting.com" class="twitter-timeline-link" target="_blank" title="http://RepositoryHosting.com" ><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="js-display-url">RepositoryHosting.com</span><span class="invisible"></span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible">&nbsp;</span></span></a> was not affected by <a href="/hashtag/Heartbleed?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" ><s>#</s><b>Heartbleed</b></a>, as we were not running a vulnerable version of OpenSSL.</p>

<p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--26px js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Check out our latest new features: http://repositoryhosting.com/blog.  We also have a major system upgrade this weekend.</p>

<div class="ProfileHeaderCard">
<h1 class="ProfileHeaderCard-name">
<a href="/rephosting"
class="ProfileHeaderCard-nameLink u-textInheritColor js-nav
">Repository Hosting</a>
</h1>

<h2 class="ProfileHeaderCard-screenname u-inlineBlock u-dir" dir="ltr">
<a class="ProfileHeaderCard-screennameLink u-linkComplex js-nav" href="/rephosting">@<span class="u-linkComplex-target">rephosting</span></a>
</h2>

<p class="ProfileHeaderCard-bio u-dir"

dir="ltr">We are an online hosting service for software project management tools. We specialize in hosting Trac, Subversion, Git, and Mercurial repositories.</p>

<p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--16px js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Fortunately, <a href="http://t.co/ifELQndFxp" rel="nofollow" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="http://RepositoryHosting.com" class="twitter-timeline-link" target="_blank" title="http://RepositoryHosting.com" ><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="js-display-url">RepositoryHosting.com</span><span class="invisible"></span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible">&nbsp;</span></span></a> was not affected by <a href="/hashtag/Heartbleed?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" ><s>#</s><b>Heartbleed</b></a>, as we were not running a vulnerable version of OpenSSL.</p>

<p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--26px js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Check out our latest new features: http://repositoryhosting.com/blog.  We also have a major system upgrade this weekend.</p>

<div class="ProfileHeaderCard">
<h1 class="ProfileHeaderCard-name">
<a href="/rephosting"
class="ProfileHeaderCard-nameLink u-textInheritColor js-nav
">Repository Hosting</a>
</h1>

<h2 class="ProfileHeaderCard-screenname u-inlineBlock u-dir" dir="ltr">
<a class="ProfileHeaderCard-screennameLink u-linkComplex js-nav" href="/rephosting">@<span class="u-linkComplex-target">rephosting</span></a>
</h2>

<p class="ProfileHeaderCard-bio u-dir"

dir="ltr">We are an online hosting service for software project management tools. We specialize in hosting Trac, Subversion, Git, and Mercurial repositories.</p>

<p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--16px js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Fortunately, <a href="http://t.co/ifELQndFxp" rel="nofollow" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="http://RepositoryHosting.com" class="twitter-timeline-link" target="_blank" title="http://RepositoryHosting.com" ><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="js-display-url">RepositoryHosting.com</span><span class="invisible"></span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible">&nbsp;</span></span></a> was not affected by <a href="/hashtag/Heartbleed?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" ><s>#</s><b>Heartbleed</b></a>, as we were not running a vulnerable version of OpenSSL.</p>

<p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--26px js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Check out our latest new features: http://repositoryhosting.com/blog.  We also have a major system upgrade this weekend.</p>

<div class="ProfileHeaderCard">
<h1 class="ProfileHeaderCard-name">
<a href="/rephosting"
class="ProfileHeaderCard-nameLink u-textInheritColor js-nav
">Repository Hosting</a>
</h1>

<h2 class="ProfileHeaderCard-screenname u-inlineBlock u-dir" dir="ltr">
<a class="ProfileHeaderCard-screennameLink u-linkComplex js-nav" href="/rephosting">@<span class="u-linkComplex-target">rephosting</span></a>
</h2>

<p class="ProfileHeaderCard-bio u-dir"

dir="ltr">We are an online hosting service for software project management tools. We specialize in hosting Trac, Subversion, Git, and Mercurial repositories.</p>

<p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--16px js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Fortunately, <a href="http://t.co/ifELQndFxp" rel="nofollow" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="http://RepositoryHosting.com" class="twitter-timeline-link" target="_blank" title="http://RepositoryHosting.com" ><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="js-display-url">RepositoryHosting.com</span><span class="invisible"></span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible">&nbsp;</span></span></a> was not affected by <a href="/hashtag/Heartbleed?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" ><s>#</s><b>Heartbleed</b></a>, as we were not running a vulnerable version of OpenSSL.</p>

<p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--26px js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Check out our latest new features: http://repositoryhosting.com/blog.  We also have a major system upgrade this weekend.</p>

<div class="ProfileHeaderCard">
<h1 class="ProfileHeaderCard-name">
<a href="/rephosting"
class="ProfileHeaderCard-nameLink u-textInheritColor js-nav
">Repository Hosting</a>
</h1>

<h2 class="ProfileHeaderCard-screenname u-inlineBlock u-dir" dir="ltr">
<a class="ProfileHeaderCard-screennameLink u-linkComplex js-nav" href="/rephosting">@<span class="u-linkComplex-target">rephosting</span></a>
</h2>

<p class="ProfileHeaderCard-bio u-dir"

dir="ltr">We are an online hosting service for software project management tools. We specialize in hosting Trac, Subversion, Git, and Mercurial repositories.</p>

<p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--16px js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Fortunately, <a href="http://t.co/ifELQndFxp" rel="nofollow" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="http://RepositoryHosting.com" class="twitter-timeline-link" target="_blank" title="http://RepositoryHosting.com" ><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="js-display-url">RepositoryHosting.com</span><span class="invisible"></span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible">&nbsp;</span></span></a> was not affected by <a href="/hashtag/Heartbleed?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" ><s>#</s><b>Heartbleed</b></a>, as we were not running a vulnerable version of OpenSSL.</p>

<p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--26px js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Check out our latest new features: http://repositoryhosting.com/blog.  We also have a major system upgrade this weekend.</p>
